data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT MC.ClaimCode,MC.EmployeeName,MC.Position,C.Duration,MC.TotalAmount,C.Province,C.Description,C.Invoice,C.NonInvoice,C.Amount, DAY(CONVERT(DATE, MC.FromDate)) AS FromDate,DAY(ToDate) AS ToDate, DAY(ClaimDate) AS ClaimDate,dbo.getMonthKH(ClaimDate) AS ClaimKH, dbo.getMonthKH(ToDate) AS TMONTHKH, YEAR(FromDate) AS FromYear, YEAR(ToDate) AS ToYear, YEAR(ClaimDate) AS ClaimYear, dbo.getMonthKH(FromDate) AS FMONTHKH, TotalAmountUS = dbo.fnNumberToWordKH(TotalAmount, 'US'), TotalAmountKh = dbo.fnNumberToWordKH(TotalAmount, 'KHR'), Amountkh= dbo.fnNumberToWordKH( Amount, 'KHR'), AmountUs= dbo.fnNumberToWordKH(Amount,'US') FROM HRMissionClaim MC LEFT JOIN HRMissionClaimItem C on C.ClaimCode=MC.ClaimCode WHERE MC.ClaimCode= @ClaimCode;
